title: Six Lessons My Ex Taught Me!
itunes:title: Six Lessons My Ex Taught Me!
description:
In this episode, Kimberly Cobb talks about meeting a cute cowboy (!!!), vents about the the skinny trend, updates us on her weekly YouTube vlogging series, shares six lessons that her ex taught her, and more!

 

Follow for weekly episodes of the "My Lips Aren't Sealed" podcast, where I discuss dating, fashion, entertainment, travel, pop culture, and more from my life! Thanks for listening!
